column5: Going to Route Lake ( Dryden area ) for the first time. Anyone been there that can tell us what to expect for fishing ? Know the lake contains walleyes and pike. Would very much appreciate any help. Thanks. Almost forgot, will be there 1st week of July.
We were there several years ago. Email me and I'll try to tell you what I know about this camp. I may still have a map around here some place.Pooch in Central Illinois
